==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Slepez
<hw>Sle*pez"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Russ.
<ets>sliepets'</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A burrowing rodent
(<spn>Spalax typhlus</spn>), native of Russia and Asia Minor. It has the
general appearance of a mole, and is destitute of eyes. Called also
<altname>mole rat</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slept</ent>⟦br⟧
